text:
Self taught makeup artist and body painter Alexys Fleming of Madeyewlook has created an amusing timelapse video where she takes us through the process of sticking a whole lot of googly eyes all over her face a upper torso.

A post shared by Lex ???? Madeyewlook (@madeyewlook) on Mar 23, 2017 at 7:55pm PDT
